{"message":"fix(remediation): Fix invalid port name "значок" in vigil-app readiness probe

The Deployment manifest contained an invalid port name "значок" (Cyrillic characters) in the readiness probe, which violates Kubernetes validation rules that require port names to contain only alphanumeric characters and hyphens.

Changed port value from "значок" to 80 (numeric port) to comply with Kubernetes validation."}
